snippet.title: Luigi's Mansion Dark Moon - Switch Teaser Trailer | Nintendo Direct 2023
snippet.description: A visually enhanced version of 3DS game Luigi's Mansion 2 is on its way to the Nintendo Switch in 2023. Get a first look at gameplay here!
